{"tid":1269873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃耀明反駁譚詠麟: 「自欺欺人」","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T09:57:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":153,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f44c9a4edd408a84479415e5e79ba3d760985c","tid":1269873,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190630/59775114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59775114&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=d19fda9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59775114&h=77213b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190630/59775114</a><br />\n<br />\n 2019年06月30日<br />\n【引渡惡法】譚詠麟撐警稱不談政治 黃耀明反駁：你踏進這個公園已非常政治 <br />\n<br />\n30年前六月四日，寫下近代中國令人痛心一頁，香港藝人發起《民主歌聲獻中華》聲援學生，出席藝人多不勝數，今日有份出席的撐警集會的譚詠麟，當年亦有份在台上演出。30年後，仍在六四燭光晚會上的，只剩下黃耀明。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>譚詠麟今日在集會中，講到不想談政治，30年前曾於阿倫同台的黃耀明，今晚在IG發文開導，明哥指譚詠麟口中的「不想談政治」是自欺欺人：「不想談政治？當你踏進這個公園，踏上這個舞台就已經非常政治，何況你不談政治，政治會找上門，所以不要掩耳盜鈴，自欺欺人。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n而對於譚詠麟在集會上提到「再咁落去，香港無得救。再搞落去無人管治到香港。」明哥亦反擊說：「法治的社會不單是靠警方維持，警方只是執法機關；法治是一個獨立公正的司法系統，其核心是獨立公正的法院審訊。警察有過大的權力或濫用權力，香港將會變成一個Police State警察社會，然後就變成極權統治，跟法西斯一樣。極！度！危！險！」"},{"pid":"0f9328ef51b992c5baea5475dc3a034b50e041d4","tid":1269873,"uid":256014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　譚詠麟</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color: green;\">明哥黃耀明（達明一派）</span><span style=\"color: red;\">同屬</span><span style=\"color: green;\">環球，</span>估唔到<span style=\"color: green;\">環球</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">可以</span><span style=\"color: red;\">包容</span>不同<span style=\"color: purple;\">政治理念</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">之</span><span style=\"color: green;\">歌星。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0dc1e09a850c0d54bf9e9f99ba839261a4b59bc7","tid":1269873,"uid":269159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wpa9Z1FjjKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fwpa9Z1FjjKo&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5756e827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wpa9Z1FjjKo</a>"},{"pid":"c79a0c4e5d7a18b4c7c63468be72f83068a3430e","tid":1269873,"uid":86628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"其實呢班偽人係自發去定點"},{"pid":"2c8f8df4e7308a066cb05d1c8120182577d169f7","tid":1269873,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14731cdf859f38a7a8fabbf273593d4c8462a4ae","tid":1269873,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c79a0c4e5d7a18b4c7c63468be72f83068a3430e","tid":1269873,"uid":86628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"其實呢班偽人係自發去定點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"可能當一個show錢咁計<br />\n好過開左倫右李"},{"pid":"633a14f34094a523311a2dbd4894c78e387e0cc8","tid":1269873,"uid":267869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:59:56.000Z","msg":"啲廢人廢噏有咩好反駁吖<br />\n明哥慳返啖氣好過啦"},{"pid":"e6ebccb957dc0cf2047f310a064b57496ff4e53a","tid":1269873,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f9328ef51b992c5baea5475dc3a034b50e041d4","tid":1269873,"uid":256014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　譚詠麟</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color